txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Dusky wings from birds and bats in western Bree-land and the Old Forest. Deliver the items to Second-watcher Heathstraw at the Boar Fountain in Bree.
'I believe that this fulfills the request. Thank you.'
'According to the request, these wings have a number of uses. If you fill it, it will be worth your while.'
Men of Bree Task:  Dusky Wings
Second-watcher Heathstraw is offering compensation for the collection of dusky wings from birds and bats in western Bree-land and the Old Forest.
Deliver the dusky wings to Second-watcher Heathstraw

You have been tasked with finding dusky wings from the birds in western Bree-land and bats in the Old Forest. Second-watcher Heathstraw awaits the delivery of these items at the Boar Fountain in Bree.
Wanted: Dusky wings from birds and bats in western Bree-land and the Old Forest.
